-- Russian Standard Vodka to Sell Ian Macleod’s Whisky Locally
-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 2012-01-24T09:15:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-24/russian-standard-vodka-to-sell-ian-macleod-s-whisky-locally.html
Billionaire Roustam Tariko’s Russian
Standard vodka brand said today it will distribute Ian Macleod
Distillers’ whisky in  Russia .  ZAO Rust Ink., a company in Russian Standard’s group,
signed a five-year contract with the British distiller and won
the right in Russia to sell King Robert II and Hedges & Butler
Royal De Luxe whisky, Russian Standard said in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow at 
 msysoyeva@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net  